A4.text: Including the class of 2025, there have been 1,111 players and 237 coaches selected for enshrinement in the College Football Hall of Fame.

A5.text: Including the 2019 class, there were 1,010 players enshrined in the College Football Hall of Fame.

A6.text: As of 2025, there are a total of 382 members of the Hall of Fame.
